jif.visit

Class LabelSubstitutionVisitor

  • java.lang.Object
    • polyglot.visit.NodeVisitor
      • jif.visit.LabelSubstitutionVisitor
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.lang.Cloneable, polyglot.util.Copy<polyglot.visit.NodeVisitor>

    public class LabelSubstitutionVisitor
extends polyglot.visit.NodeVisitor
    Visits an AST, and applies a LabelSubstitution to all labels that occur in the AST. The LabelSubstitution is not allowed to throw any SemanticExceptions.
